l="" class="menu-membership__list-item-link" href="/membership/newsletters"><span>Manage Newsletters</span></a></li><li class="menu-membership__list-item"><a aria-label="" class="menu-membership__list-item-link" href="https://thedailybeast.freshdesk.com/support/solutions" target="_blank"><span>Need Help?</span></a></li><li class="menu-membership__list-item"><button class="menu-membership__logout" type="button" aria-label="Log Out">LogOut</button></li></ul><div class="Menu__outside-area"></div></div></div></nav><div class="recirc-block TDB article"></div><div class="back-to-homepage"><a href="/"><span class="icomoon icon-circle-left-arrow"></span>HOMEPAGE</a></div><div class="ad-wrap ad-wrap---article-header "><div id="arcad-feature-f0f89sybeuD82iS-c9fe2e76e82ed" class="c-stack tdb-ads-block" data-style-direction="vertical" data-style-justification="start" data-style-alignment="center" data-style-inline="false" data-style-wrap="nowrap"><div class="ad-block-unit-wrapper" data-testid="ad-block-unit-wrapper"><div id="-article-header" class="ad-unit-wrapper"></div></div></div></div></header><section role="main" id="main" tabindex="-1" class="b-right-rail__main"><div class="c-stack b-right-rail__full-width-1" data-style-direction="vertical" data-style-justification="start" data-style-alignment="unset" data-style-inline="false" data-style-wrap="nowrap"></div><div class="c-grid b-right-rail__rail-container"><div class="c-stack b-right-rail__main-interior-item" data-style-direction="vertical" data-style-justification="start" data-style-alignment="unset" data-style-inline="false" data-style-wrap="nowrap"><a class="c-overline b-overline TDB" href="/category/politics/"><span>Politics<!-- --> <i class="icomoon icon-menu-arrow-obs"></i></span></a><h1 class="b-headline">Trump Accused of Sharing Bogus Video of Deadly Drug Boat Strike</h1><div class="Rubric"><div class="Rubric__content">STRIKING CLAIM</div><div class="Rubric__divider"><div class="Rubric__divider__bottom"></div></div></div><h2 class="c-heading b-subheadline">A Venezuelan official said the video the president gloated about was “generated by AI.”</h2><undefined class="c-stack b-double-chain" data-style-direction="vertical"><undefined class="c-grid b-double-chain__children-grid"><undefined class="c-stack b-double-chain__child-item" data-style-direction="vertical"><div class="Article-byline--single-author"><div class="Article-byline--single-author__container "><div class="Article-byline--single-author__author" itemScope="" itemType="https://schema.org/Person"><a class="Article-byline--single-author__author-image" href="/author/ewan-palmer"><img alt="Ewan Palmer" src="https://author-service-images-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub/thedailybeast/UUN5LNQHUVFILIPWJ3MSQZE5BE.jpg" itemProp="image" loading="lazy"/></a><div class="Article-byline--single-author__author-info"><a class="Article-byline--single-author__author-link" href="/author/ewan-palmer"><span class="Article-byline--single-author__author-name" itemProp="name">Ewan Palmer<span> </span></span></a><a class="Article-byline--single-author__author-link" href="/author/ewan-palmer"><p class="Article-byline--single-author__author-role" itemProp="jobTitle">Reporter</p></a></div><span class="Separator"></span></div></div><div class="PublicationTime"><time class="PublicationTime__pub-time" dateTime="September 03, 2025 at 10:58AM EDT"><span class="PublicationTime__date-label">Published<!-- --> </span><span class="PublicationTime__date">Sep. 3 2025<!-- --> </span><span class="PublicationTime__time">10:58AM EDT<!-- --> </span></time></div></div></undefined><undefined class="c-stack b-double-chain__child-item" data-style-direction="vertical"><div class="c-stack b-share-bar" data-style-direction="vertical" data-style-justification="center" data-style-alignment="center" data-style-inline="false" data-style-wrap="nowrap"><button aria-label="Share current article via %{socialType}" class="c-button c-button--comments c-button--tdb"><span><div class="c-button__content"><img alt="comments icon" class="c-image b-share-bar__icon b-share-bar__icon--comments" src="/pf/resources/svgs/common/comment.svg?d=374"/><span id="comment-counter" class="c-button__content__count" data-spotim-module="messages-count" data-post-id="4HD54FLNZFC4FKXQMK75DPIRV4" real-time="true"></span><span id="comment-counter-text">Comments</span></div></span></button><button aria-label="Share current article via Facebook" class="c-button"><span><img alt="fb icon" class="c-image b-share-bar__icon" src="/pf/resources/svgs/social-logos/fb.svg?d=374"/></span></button><button aria-label="Share current article via Twitter" class="c-button"><span><img alt="twitter icon" class="c-image b-share-bar__icon" src="/pf/resources/svgs/social-logos/twitter-icon.svg?d=374"/></span></button><button aria-label="Share current article via Email" class="c-button"><span><img alt="email icon" class="c-image b-share-bar__icon" src="/pf/resources/svgs/social-logos/email-icon.svg?d=374"/></span></button><button aria-label="Share current article via Reddit" class="c-button"><span><img alt="reddit icon" class="c-image b-share-bar__icon" src="/pf/resources/svgs/social-logos/reddit.svg?d=374"/></span></button></div></undefined></undefined></undefined><div class="b-lead-art"><figure class="c-media-item b-lead-art__video-iframe-container"><iframe src="https://cdn.jwplayer.com/players/DwIYeAeh-AjIcq1uW.html" title=""></iframe></figure></div><section id="newsletter-unit" class="newsletter-unit" aria-labelledby="newsletter-title"></section><div class="b-article-body"><article id="main-article" class=""><p class="c-paragraph">President Donald Trump has been accused of sharing an AI-generated video showing a U.S. military airstrike targeting a boat allegedly carrying drugs from Venezuela.</p><p class="c-paragraph">Freddy Nanez, Venezuela’s communications minister, suggested that the clip Trump <a onclick="_sendArticleBodyInlineLinkClickAnalytics('https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/posts/115136798909755892')" href="https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/posts/115136798909755892" target="_self" rel="" title="https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/posts/115136798909755892">posted</a> on Truth Social, which is believed to show the moment that 11 people were killed during a strike in international waters, was fake and looked “cartoonish.”</p><div><p class="c-paragraph">Trump announced Tuesday that the U.S. military had hit the boat at a White House briefing that was the president’s first official public appearance in a week amid speculation about <a onclick="_sendArticleBodyInlineLinkClickAnalytics('https://www.thedailybeast.com/trump79-cakes-bruised-hand-in-makeup-after-vanishing-for-days/')" href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/trump79-cakes-bruised-hand-in-makeup-after-vanishing-for-days/" target="_self" rel="" title="https://www.thedailybeast.com/trump79-cakes-bruised-hand-in-makeup-after-vanishing-for-days/">the 79-year-old’s health.</a></p></div><figure class="c-media-item b-article-body__image"><img data-chromatic="ignore" alt="Black and white image of boat riding on the ocean." class="c-image" src="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/6DBRDRKKVZB7VEKKRH35SCZD7M.jpg?auth=cd4ff2a7ebc6f1d0d96f25482256808ed551b4d6812d54b442202e938c3b83df&amp;width=800&amp;height=400" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/6DBRDRKKVZB7VEKKRH35SCZD7M.jpg?auth=cd4ff2a7ebc6f1d0d96f25482256808ed551b4d6812d54b442202e938c3b83df&amp;width=800&amp;height=400 800w, https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/6DBRDRKKVZB7VEKKRH35SCZD7M.jpg?auth=cd4ff2a7ebc6f1d0d96f25482256808ed551b4d6812d54b442202e938c3b83df&amp;width=1024&amp;height=512 1024w, https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/6DBRDRKKVZB7VEKKRH35SCZD7M.jpg?auth=cd4ff2a7ebc6f1d0d96f25482256808ed551b4d6812d54b442202e938c3b83df&amp;width=1440&amp;height=720 1440w" width="800" height="400"/><figcaption class="c-media-item__fig-caption"><span class="c-media-item__caption">Donald Trump told reporters at the Oval Office the U.S. had “shot out a drug-carrying boat” coming from Venezuela. </span><span class="c-media-item__credit">Truth Social/Donald Trump </span></figcaption></figure><p class="c-paragraph">Trump claimed the people targeted on the boat were members of the Tren de Aragua gang, which the U.S. designated a terrorist group in February. </p><p class="c-paragraph">He also shared the video of the vessel being struck at sea, accompanied by the typically unhinged warning: “Please let this serve as notice to anybody even thinking about bringing drugs into the United States of America. BEWARE! Thank you for your attention to this matter!!!!!!!!!!!”</p><div><div class="fancylink-card"><div class="fancylink-card__content"><a href="/trump-accuses-putin-of-plot-against-america-in-bonkers-post/" aria-label="/trump-accuses-putin-of-plot-against-america-in-bonkers-post/"><span class="fancylink-card__title">Trump Accuses Putin of Plot Against America in Bonkers Post</span></a><a href="/trump-accuses-putin-of-plot-against-america-in-bonkers-post/" aria-label="/trump-accuses-putin-of-plot-against-america-in-bonkers-post/" class="fancylink-card__rubric fancylink-card__rubric-tdb"><span>CONSPIRACY THEORY</span></a><div class="fancylink-card__authors-box"><a href="/author/catherine-bouris"><span class="fancylink-card__authors-box--name">Catherine Bouris</span></a></div></div><a href="/trump-accuses-putin-of-plot-against-america-in-bonkers-post/" aria-label="/trump-accuses-putin-of-plot-against-america-in-bonkers-post/"><picture class="c-picture"><source alt="Trump" responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(max-width: 375px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/5W47ZV6UFBEVPATOROPK6XCXPI.jpg?auth=b5f63f67d632244e437793bd6e21a43f01ac42b58be37dd6f7268c627d267edf&amp;smart=true&amp;width=400" width="400"/><source alt="Trump" responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(max-width: 500px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/5W47ZV6UFBEVPATOROPK6XCXPI.jpg?auth=b5f63f67d632244e437793bd6e21a43f01ac42b58be37dd6f7268c627d267edf&amp;smart=true&amp;width=600" width="600"/><source alt="Trump" responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(max-width: 703px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/5W47ZV6UFBEVPATOROPK6XCXPI.jpg?auth=b5f63f67d632244e437793bd6e21a43f01ac42b58be37dd6f7268c627d267edf&amp;smart=true&amp;width=800" width="800"/><source alt="Trump" responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(max-width: 900px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/5W47ZV6UFBEVPATOROPK6XCXPI.jpg?auth=b5f63f67d632244e437793bd6e21a43f01ac42b58be37dd6f7268c627d267edf&amp;smart=true&amp;width=1000" width="1000"/><source alt="Trump" responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(max-width: 1031px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/5W47ZV6UFBEVPATOROPK6XCXPI.jpg?auth=b5f63f67d632244e437793bd6e21a43f01ac42b58be37dd6f7268c627d267edf&amp;smart=true&amp;width=1200" width="1200"/><source alt="Trump" responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(min-width: 1032px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/5W47ZV6UFBEVPATOROPK6XCXPI.jpg?auth=b5f63f67d632244e437793bd6e21a43f01ac42b58be37dd6f7268c627d267edf&amp;smart=true&amp;width=1400" width="1400"/><img aria-label="" data-chromatic="ignore" alt="Trump" class="c-image fancylink-card__image" loading="lazy" src="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/5W47ZV6UFBEVPATOROPK6XCXPI.jpg?auth=b5f63f67d632244e437793bd6e21a43f01ac42b58be37dd6f7268c627d267edf&amp;smart=true&amp;width=300" width="300"/></picture></a></div></div><p class="c-paragraph">Nanez has now said the video, which was also shared online by several Trump administration officials, including Secretary of State Marco Rubio and Defense Secretary Pete Hegseth, of being “generated by AI.”</p><p class="c-paragraph">“The video shows a ship being attacked and then exploding in a way that looks like a simplified, almost cartoonish animation, rather than a realistic depiction of an explosion,” Nanez <a onclick="_sendArticleBodyInlineLinkClickAnalytics('https://www.instagram.com/p/DOHiirbEV6a/?hl=en&amp;img_index=1')" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DOHiirbEV6a/?hl=en&amp;img_index=1" target="_self" rel="" title="https://www.instagram.com/p/DOHiirbEV6a/?hl=en&amp;img_index=1">wrote</a> on social media.</p><div class="ad-wrap ad-wrap--openweb-iau "><div class="ad__openweb-iau-slot tdb-ads-block" data-openweb-ad="true" data-row="1" data-column="1"></div><div class="ad-wrap ad-wrap---openweb-article-1 ad-wrap--hide"><div id="arcad-feature-f0fwNn8N3NiFd3-60e8f96f15ae7" class="c-stack tdb-ads-block" data-style-direction="vertical" data-style-justification="start" data-style-alignment="center" data-style-inline="false" data-style-wrap="nowrap"><div class="ad-block-unit-wrapper" data-testid="ad-block-unit-wrapper"><div id="-openweb-article-1" class="ad-unit-wrapper"></div></div></div></div></div><p class="c-paragraph">“The video contains motion artifacts and a lack of realistic detail, which is common in AI-generated videos. The water, in particular, looks very stylized and unnatural,” he added.</p><figure class="c-media-item b-article-body__image"><img data-chromatic="ignore" alt="Defense Secretary Pete Hegseth (R) looks on as U.S. President Donald Trump speaks in the Oval Office at the White House on September 02, 2025 in Washington, DC." class="c-image" src="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/WJ4NU75IIRH55FWQTCKUHMQFZU.jpg?auth=88ae3d07864e785eb376413615aa59e1aeb1f8dd91829ca8a49576952c002e7f&amp;width=800&amp;height=533" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/WJ4NU75IIRH55FWQTCKUHMQFZU.jpg?auth=88ae3d07864e785eb376413615aa59e1aeb1f8dd91829ca8a49576952c002e7f&amp;width=800&amp;height=533 800w, https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/WJ4NU75IIRH55FWQTCKUHMQFZU.jpg?auth=88ae3d07864e785eb376413615aa59e1aeb1f8dd91829ca8a49576952c002e7f&amp;width=1024&amp;height=682 1024w, https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/WJ4NU75IIRH55FWQTCKUHMQFZU.jpg?auth=88ae3d07864e785eb376413615aa59e1aeb1f8dd91829ca8a49576952c002e7f&amp;width=1440&amp;height=959 1440w" width="800" height="533"/><figcaption class="c-media-item__fig-caption"><span class="c-media-item__caption">Defense Secretary Pete Hegseth also shared the clip on social media. </span><span class="c-media-item__credit">Alex Wong/Getty Images </span></figcaption></figure><p class="c-paragraph">News agency <a onclick="_sendArticleBodyInlineLinkClickAnalytics('https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/us-military-kills-11-people-strike-alleged-drug-boat-venezuela-trump-says-2025-09-03/')" href="https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/us-military-kills-11-people-strike-alleged-drug-boat-venezuela-trump-says-2025-09-03/" target="_self" rel="" title="https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/us-military-kills-11-people-strike-alleged-drug-boat-venezuela-trump-says-2025-09-03/">Reuters</a> said it conducted independent checks on the video and found no evidence of manipulation. Reuters added that thorough verification “is an ongoing process” and that it will continue to review the footage as more information becomes available.</p><p class="c-paragraph">While not addressing the AI claims specifically, John Feeley, a former U.S. ambassador to Panama who worked in anti-drug operations in Latin America, said the video shared by the Trump administration does not align with standard Coast Guard protocol for stopping boats believed to be carrying narcotics.</p><p class="c-paragraph">“Everything is done to preserve life,” Feeley told <a onclick="_sendArticleBodyInlineLinkClickAnalytics('https://www.wsj.com/politics/national-security/u-s-military-strikes-drug-vessel-from-venezuela-killing-11-19661cc9?mod=hp_lead_pos11')" href="https://www.wsj.com/politics/national-security/u-s-military-strikes-drug-vessel-from-venezuela-killing-11-19661cc9?mod=hp_lead_pos11" target="_self" rel="" title="https://www.wsj.com/politics/national-security/u-s-military-strikes-drug-vessel-from-venezuela-killing-11-19661cc9?mod=hp_lead_pos11"><i>The Wall Street Journal</i>.</a> “What we don’t do is just shoot up boats like Netflix likes to pretend. We can shoot in self-defense, but we rarely do that because most narcos just give up.”</p><p class="c-paragraph">The Pentagon referred a request for comment from the Daily Beast to the White House, who did not immediately respond.</p><div><div class="fancylink-card"><div class="fancylink-card__content"><a href="/trump-hit-with-humiliating-loss-as-court-blows-up-his-unlawful-alien-enemies-act-deportation-plot/" aria-label="/trump-hit-with-humiliating-loss-as-court-blows-up-his-unlawful-alien-enemies-act-deportation-plot/"><span class="fancylink-card__title">Trump Hit With Humiliating Court Loss on Trademark Policy</span></a><a href="/trump-hit-with-humiliating-loss-as-court-blows-up-his-unlawful-alien-enemies-act-deportation-plot/" aria-label="/trump-hit-with-humiliating-loss-as-court-blows-up-his-unlawful-alien-enemies-act-deportation-plot/" class="fancylink-card__rubric fancylink-card__rubric-tdb"><span>SLAP IN THE FACE</span></a><div class="fancylink-card__authors-box"><a href="/author/janna-brancolini"><span class="fancylink-card__authors-box--name">Janna Brancolini</span></a></div></div><a href="/trump-hit-with-humiliating-loss-as-court-blows-up-his-unlawful-alien-enemies-act-deportation-plot/" aria-label="/trump-hit-with-humiliating-loss-as-court-blows-up-his-unlawful-alien-enemies-act-deportation-plot/"><picture class="c-picture"><source alt="Donald Trump reacts to a question during a Cabinet meeting at the White House." responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(max-width: 375px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/LEY22BXBZBDCFPABFR2BJ3X6JA.jpg?auth=2688fcd444510099a574325c588431c53869104330ed6c1717fe13d58326bd55&amp;smart=true&amp;width=400" width="400"/><source alt="Donald Trump reacts to a question during a Cabinet meeting at the White House." responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(max-width: 500px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/LEY22BXBZBDCFPABFR2BJ3X6JA.jpg?auth=2688fcd444510099a574325c588431c53869104330ed6c1717fe13d58326bd55&amp;smart=true&amp;width=600" width="600"/><source alt="Donald Trump reacts to a question during a Cabinet meeting at the White House." responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(max-width: 703px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/LEY22BXBZBDCFPABFR2BJ3X6JA.jpg?auth=2688fcd444510099a574325c588431c53869104330ed6c1717fe13d58326bd55&amp;smart=true&amp;width=800" width="800"/><source alt="Donald Trump reacts to a question during a Cabinet meeting at the White House." responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(max-width: 900px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/LEY22BXBZBDCFPABFR2BJ3X6JA.jpg?auth=2688fcd444510099a574325c588431c53869104330ed6c1717fe13d58326bd55&amp;smart=true&amp;width=1000" width="1000"/><source alt="Donald Trump reacts to a question during a Cabinet meeting at the White House." responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(max-width: 1031px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/LEY22BXBZBDCFPABFR2BJ3X6JA.jpg?auth=2688fcd444510099a574325c588431c53869104330ed6c1717fe13d58326bd55&amp;smart=true&amp;width=1200" width="1200"/><source alt="Donald Trump reacts to a question during a Cabinet meeting at the White House." responsiveImages="" sizes="" media="(min-width: 1032px)" srcSet="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/LEY22BXBZBDCFPABFR2BJ3X6JA.jpg?auth=2688fcd444510099a574325c588431c53869104330ed6c1717fe13d58326bd55&amp;smart=true&amp;width=1400" width="1400"/><img aria-label="" data-chromatic="ignore" alt="Donald Trump reacts to a question during a Cabinet meeting at the White House." class="c-image fancylink-card__image" loading="lazy" src="https://www.thedailybeast.com/resizer/v2/LEY22BXBZBDCFPABFR2BJ3X6JA.jpg?auth=2688fcd444510099a574325c588431c53869104330ed6c1717fe13d58326bd55&amp;smart=true&amp;width=300" width="300"/></picture></a></div></div><p class="c-paragraph">Elsewhere on Tuesday, Trump suggested that bizarre viral footage showing items being launched from a White House window was “probably AI-generated,” claiming the building’s windows cannot be opened because they are all <a onclick="_sendArticleBodyInlineLinkClickAnalytics('https://www.thedailybeast.com/trump-gives-bonkers-explanation-for-white-house-window-video/')" href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/trump-gives-bonkers-explanation-for-white-house-window-video/" target="_self" rel="" title="https://www.thedailybeast.com/trump-gives-bonkers-explanation-for-white-house-window-video/">“heavily armored and bullet-proofed.”</a></p><div><p class="c-paragraph">That statement directly contradicts an earlier explanation from the White House, which said the <a onclick="_sendArticleBodyInlineLinkClickAnalytics('https://www.thedailybeast.com/white-house-reveals-why-mystery-objects-were-thrown-out-window/')" href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/white-house-reveals-why-mystery-objects-were-thrown-out-window/" target="_self" rel="" title="https://www.thedailybeast.com/white-house-reveals-why-mystery-objects-were-thrown-out-window/">video was genuine</a> and showed “a contractor who was doing regular maintenance while the President was gone.”</p></div></article></div><div class="Short-author-bio-tips"><div class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios"><span class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-border"></span><div class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio" itemScope="" itemType="https://schema.org/Person"><a class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-image-link" href="/author/ewan-palmer"><img alt="Ewan Palmer" src="https://author-service-images-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub/thedailybeast/UUN5LNQHUVFILIPWJ3MSQZE5BE.jpg" itemProp="image" loading="lazy"/></a><div class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-metadata"><a class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-metadata-name-link" href="/author/ewan-palmer"><h3 class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-metadata-name-text" itemProp="name">Ewan Palmer</h3></a><a class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-metadata-job-title-link" href="/author/ewan-palmer"><p class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-metadata-job-title-text" itemProp="jobTitle">Reporter</p></a><div class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-metadata-social-links"><a class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-metadata-social-links-email" href="mailto:ewan.palmer@thedailybeast.com" itemProp="email"><p class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-metadata-social-links-email-text">ewan.palmer@thedailybeast.com</p></a></div></div></div><span class="Short-author-bio-tips__bios-bio-border"></span></div><p class="Short-author-bio-tips__tip">Got a tip? Send it to The Daily Beast<!-- --> <a class="Short-author-bio-tips__tip-link" href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/tips">here</a>.</p><span class="border"></span></div><div id="user-comments" class="comments-block__wrap"><div class="comments-block comments-block--loading " data-spotim-module="conversation"></div></div></div><aside id="right-rail" class="c-stack b-right-rail__main-right-rail" data-style-direction="vertical" data-style-justification="start" data-style-alignment="unset" data-style-inline="false" data-style-wrap="nowrap"><div class="trending-now"><span class="trending-now--title">Trending Now</span><div class="trending-now--section-title"><div class="section-title--container"><div class="obsessed section-title section-title--alignment-center section-title__border--two-lines-single-double "><div class="section-title--content"></div></div></div></div><div><div class="card-3-container "><div class="card-3-container--article-summary"><span class="card-3-container--article-summary__swipe swipe--media badge" aria-label="media">media</span><a aria-label="MAGA-Coded CBS Anchor’s Ratings Debacle Spirals" href="/maga-coded-cbs-anchor-tony-dokoupils-ratings-debacle-spirals//"><span class="card-3-container--article-summary__headline">MAGA-Coded CBS Anchor’s Ratings Debacle Spirals</span></a><div class="card-3-container--article-summary__author"><div><span class="card-3-container--article-summary__au